data.description:
Attention investors!!  Huge living area in kitchen, two bedrooms on one end and master with a fireplace on the other, split level design.
Home is in need of some repairs.   Sellers are ready for offers.   Great room has recently been painted.    Price reduced!

The outside offers a huge deck and above ground pool.  The deck is 700 sq feet and the garage is 35 x 20 sq feet.   Sold as is.
